{"link":"https://trailhead.salesforce.com/en/modules/alignment-with-your-manager/units/move-forward-together","title":"Move Forward, Together Unit | Salesforce Trailhead","shortLink":"move-forward-together","questions":[{"title":"1How can employees show their managers that they are trustworthy?","answers":[{"content":"A Deliver projects on time and communicate if anything is off track.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"},{"content":"B Remind their managers during their 1:1s that they can be trusted.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"C Tell their manager\u0027s manager about how much great work they are doing.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"},{"content":"D Avoid discussing difficult projects and situations so they think you\u0027re on top of everything.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"wrongAnswers":[],"correctAnswer":{"content":"A Deliver projects on time and communicate if anything is off track.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(1)"},{"title":"2You are constantly looking for ways to improve and stay in step with your manager. What is one way you can check in on your biggest growth areas?","answers":[{"content":"A Send your work to an unbiased group of reviewers when you finish each project.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"},{"content":"B Communicate frequently about where you can improve.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"D Reject feedback so you can improve on your own.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"wrongAnswers":[{"content":"C Ask your manager\u0027s peers for feedback, instead of your manager.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"}],"correctAnswer":{"content":"B Communicate frequently about where you can improve.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(2)"},{"title":"3Both you and your manager have suggested approaches to solving a customer\u0027s problem. Which of the following actions can nudge your manager toward your solution?","answers":[{"content":"A Insist that your idea is better.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(2)"},{"content":"B Ask someone else to be a tie breaker and select the better project.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(3)"},{"content":"D Show how what you want to do advances your boss\u0027s goals.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"}],"wrongAnswers":[{"content":"C Use reverse psychology to say your manager\u0027s idea is better than yours.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(4)"}],"correctAnswer":{"content":"D Show how what you want to do advances your boss\u0027s goals.","selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3) \u003e div.question_answer.clearfix:nth-child(5)"},"selector":"#challenge \u003e section.challenge-section.challenge-section-container.quiz \u003e div.bottom-section \u003e div.questions \u003e div.question:nth-child(3)"}]}